{"tid":2057732,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港虛擬銀行，眾安(ZA) 銀行，係紅色資本。ZA BANK送你1000蚊出賣朋友，被朋友出賣一蚊都冇，蝕埋個人資料。","createTime":"2020-06-09T15:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T11:58:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fad3ee8e3c2b8fb74fae83bd4753bffe1369cab0","tid":2057732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"本日，多個媒體推介並表示用ZA BANK(眾安銀行)收取政府發放的1萬元津貼的銀行，可再獲1000元，事實又是如何呢？其實想要優惠原來不易，<span style=\"color: red;\">首先必須要推介兩個朋友，而朋友被出賣，更是一蚊都冇，蝕埋個人資料。</span><br />\n<br />\n我們細看條款，原來這多出來的一千元，也來之不易。要得到額外的一千元，首先要是未登記過的新用戶，另外還有三個重要手續要做：<br />\n<br />\n1. 新客戶以<span style=\"color: red;\">邀請碼「 WANT11K」</span>開立ZA Bank賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n2. 新客戶<span style=\"color: red;\">必須在14日內邀請兩名朋友開戶，可獲400元現金回贈及進行下一步。</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 如新客戶再選擇ZA Bank為收取政府發放的1萬元津貼的銀行，可再獲600元現金回贈。<br />\n<br />\n這個＄1000 的領取手法，其實有點取巧，一來介紹朋友的獎賞本身就是「無上限」，介紹 1 個有＄200、介紹 10 個就有＄2000，故其實最終 ZA Bank 鐵定加碼予介紹人的，就只有＄600。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">被介紹開戶的兩個朋友，由於用的不是「萬一」邀請碼，只能夠在開戶後得到早前公布的 2％ 定期存款加息券，而在政府派發現金時則未能得到任何加成，變相其實令介紹人背上了「出賣朋友」的罪名</span>，著實需要留意。"},{"pid":"594e610bd4f1456c238565a49621d7c2ee3fc882","tid":2057732,"uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"A: 用我邀請碼登記啦，有1000蚊呀<br />\nB&amp;C: 登記咗啦，點拎1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA: 係我拎1000蚊呀，傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e29eada31015125c86bc0d65afe9f94e7b43c0","tid":2057732,"uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"岩岩拎到牌嘅虛擬眾安銀行（ZA bank），定存利息竟然高到<span style=\"color: red;\">6厘</span>，搞到我都扯扯地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkHYkxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkHYkxW.png&h=910fe7eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-01-12/hong-kong-s-first-digital-bank-offers-6-rate-that-dwarfs-hsbc-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-01-12%2Fhong-kong-s-first-digital-bank-offers-6-rate-that-dwarfs-hsbc-s&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=523a5ea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-01-12/hong-kong-s-first-digital-bank-offers-6-rate-that-dwarfs-hsbc-s</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇多少少報導，原來佢開戶同平時認證竟然係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人面辨識</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Six12N3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSix12N3.png&h=40993fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/money/other/定期存款遊戲化！眾安銀行試業存息最高68厘/ar-BBYK0mY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fmoney%2Fother%2F%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%81%E7%9C%BE%E5%AE%89%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E8%A9%A6%E6%A5%AD%E5%AD%98%E6%81%AF%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%9868%E5%8E%98%2Far-BBYK0mY&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=68022d94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/money/other/定期存款遊戲化！眾安銀行試業存息最高68厘/ar-BBYK0mY</a><br />\n<br />\n一講起人面識別，即刻諗起大陸啦，點知睇一睇背景，真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紅色資本</span></span>黎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtknNf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtknNf9.png&h=4be40ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2522674/【虛擬銀行】眾安銀行搶先開業%E3%80%80一文看清前世今生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2522674%2F%E3%80%90%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%AE%89%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E9%96%8B%E6%A5%AD%25E3%2580%2580%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%B8%85%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E4%BB%8A%E7%94%9F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=b23ab81d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2522674/【虛擬銀行】眾安銀行搶先開業%E3%80%80一文看清前世今生</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該廣傳出去，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又人面識別又紅色資本，梗係要幫手叫大家瘋狂幫襯！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9364e40df8c9d96b5aeb1a25fed4966e1b67f122","tid":2057732,"uid":470,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"咩「竟然係要人面辨識」<br />\n全地球嘅銀行remote開戶都要人面辨識架啦<br />\n屌支資ok 但唔好咁井底蛙得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438b2c03cda488beef6338192a1708159a2b187b","tid":2057732,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:22:57.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭"},{"pid":"84a7a5a13d4564e302b4f2477a55b41ffdcc3013","tid":2057732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"9364e40df8c9d96b5aeb1a25fed4966e1b67f122","tid":2057732,"uid":470,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"咩「竟然係要人面辨識」<br />\n全地球嘅銀行remote開戶都要人面辨識架啦<br />\n屌支資ok 但唔好咁井底蛙得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"其實篇野我係抄人，唔係我打"},{"pid":"fce564e15c4f4561cb0acfdb5c3ae491ca4e9b1b","tid":2057732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d82088f9894bee64b32350ed2f7b19ec41fce4a","tid":2057732,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"剩係支那兩個字已經係靠害"},{"pid":"8dda0e5317e5c1cee5823f1aebf96ea44063dceb","tid":2057732,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9364e40df8c9d96b5aeb1a25fed4966e1b67f122","tid":2057732,"uid":470,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"咩「竟然係要人面辨識」<br />\n全地球嘅銀行remote開